**Quick reference decision flowchart:**
```
START
  │
  ▼
Calculate AR delta between source and target
  │
  ▼
Can pure CROP achieve target AR?
  │
  ├─YES─► Does crop stay outside product safe zone + 5% buffer?
  │         │
  │         ├─YES─► ✅ PRIORITY 1: PURE CROP
  │         │
  │         └─NO──► Continue to hybrid evaluation
  │
  └─NO──► Calculate required outpaint expansion
            │
            ▼
          Is expansion < 15%?
            │
            ├─YES─► Can we crop the OTHER axis to reduce outpaint?
            │         │
            │         ├─YES─► ✅ PRIORITY 2: HYBRID CROP-DOMINANT
            │         │
            │         └─NO──► ✅ PRIORITY 4: PURE OUTPAINT (minimal)
            │
            └─NO──► Is expansion 15-40%?
                      │
                      ├─YES─► Is background simple/moderate?
                      │         │
                      │         ├─YES─► ✅ PRIORITY 3: HYBRID OUTPAINT-DOMINANT
                      │         │
                      │         └─NO──► ⚠️ PRIORITY 5: FLAG FOR REVIEW
                      │
                      └─NO──► Is expansion > 60%?
                                │
